message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product, which holds immense value to us and, I believe, to you as well. Given its significance, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $9,500. This is a special opportunity to acquire a product that could potentially be worth much more in the future, and I am confident it aligns with your needs and expectations. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
